:{{DIcon|Talk}} The Ambrosial Arbor is growing again...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502016201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G52/Act502016201.json-->
::'''Yinshu:''' *sigh*
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's with all the sighing?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502016204-->
::'''Yinshu:''' You are the twenty-seventh person to mention this to me today.
::'''Yinshu:''' I see, I see... Mr. Xiyan would probably be interested in this.
::'''Yinshu:''' But I'm just a kid helping out here. Hope this thing doesn't impact my work...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502016201-->
;(If {{Mission|Obsequies Performed, A Long Road Ahead|showChapter=0}} has been completed and {{Mission|Wood Sprouts Anew, Fate Tilts Askew|showChapter=0}} has been completed, {{cx}}<!--performance 502016201 has been seen-->, and {{Mission|Obsequies Performed, A Long Road Ahead|showChapter=0}} has not been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Finally, the Ambrosial Arbor crisis is over... What's your take?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502016105: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502016105.json-->
::'''Yinshu:''' Alright! Alright! Just stop with all the Ambrosial Arbor stuff!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You didn't answer my question...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wh&mdash;What's the rush?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502016305-->
::'''Yinshu:''' There have been 52 people who came to talk to me about this matter. Among them, 48 asked me whether there were readables that discussed the secrets behind the growth and ceasing of the Ambrosial Arbor.
::'''Yinshu:''' As a mere bookstore assistant, I have no say in the writing and publishing of readables... Alas... They should pester those editors instead. Anyway, I have no stock of those readables here.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502016105-->
